HAI 1.4
    I HAS A nums ITZ A BUKKIT
    nums HAS A 0 ITZ 10
    nums HAS A 1 ITZ 20
    nums HAS A 2 ITZ 30
    nums HAS A 3 ITZ 40
    nums HAS A 4 ITZ 50

    I HAS A total ITZ 0
